      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "Your pain feels so intensely personal right now, and it seems like the weight of your private agony makes external comfort unreachable. While your grief feels singular, please know that the depth of your suffering is recognized by others who are trained to listen without judgment. There are professionals who can meet you in this very dark space, offering a dignified but necessary presence. Please consider calling a crisis line; they are there specifically to witness your pain without interruption.",
